snippet.textDisplay:
Without a doubt, the best song I've heard by any Indian musician/singer/music director this year! 
WHAT A SONG!!! Kick ass stuff by Ram Sampath to begin with to come up with something like this...and then INCREDIBLE work by Bhanvari Devi and the inimitable Hard Kaur!!

And what a band! Keyboard parts, Violin (love the almost Irish vibe), percussions (the djembe bits in the start), guitars (the first entry and then the crunchy riffs later)...and drums(JAI ho!) :) 
BRILLIANT!
snippet.textOriginal:
